bilingual.source: They will dispose of the hazardous materials safely.
bilingual.target: 他们将安全处理危险材料。

bilingual.source: The factory needs to properly dispose of the sludge.
bilingual.target: 工厂需要妥善处理这些污泥。

bilingual.source: You should dispose of confidential documents securely.
bilingual.target: 你应该安全处理机密文件。

bilingual.source: Make sure to dispose of the ampule properly after use.
bilingual.target: 使用后务必妥善处理安瓿。

bilingual.source: Dispose of the waste properly to avoid a biohazard.
bilingual.target: 正确处理废物以避免生物危害。

list.abstract: dispose（英 [dɪˈspəʊz]，美 [dɪˈspoʊz]），英语单词，作动词为丢掉；处理；安置。短语搭配有dispose of（处理，处置掉）。例句为“She was forced to dispose of her art treasures.（她被迫处理了自己的艺术珍品。）”。 dispose动词类近义词有schedule、budget等，名词类近义词有make、temperament。相关反义词有indispose、disqualify。

yingyinNormal.en: Our reputation is hanging by a thread as it is. Take it away from here, far away. Kill it. Dispose of it. Go!
yingyinNormal.zh: 到时餐厅声望就会像这只老鼠一样，把它弄走，愈远愈好，杀了它，处理掉，快点。

yingyinNormal.en: You see, Lady Mary said... Lady Mary may dispose of her own clothes as she sees fit. But I do not know what gives her the right to dispose of mine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是这样，玛丽小姐说…玛丽小姐随便怎么处置她自己的衣服都行，但她凭什么随意处置我的衣服。

yingyinNormal.en: What are you thinking? I have always wanted a permit to dispose of hazardous waste. Let's do it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想干什么？人家一直想搞一张处置危险废弃物的许可证。一起去吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Still, the power of the diary began to scare her. She tried to dispose of it in the girls' bathroom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 日记的力量把她给吓坏了，于是她试着把日记丢到女厕所。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
